high_descs: Walk across the room to the white table.
Pick up the fork on the table.
Take to the counter to the left of the stove.
Put the fork in the frying pan next to the pot.
Pick up the frying pan with the fork in it.
Walk back to the white table in the corner.
Set the frying pan with fork down to the left of the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Set a frying pan with a fork in it on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and stand in front of the bottle on the white table.
Pick the fork up from the table.
Turn around and stand in front of the counter near the large pot and pan.
Put the fork in the pan on the right.
Pick the pan up from the counter.
Go  left and stand in front of the bottle on the white table.
Put the pan on the table to the left of the bottle.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a fork in it on the table.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the round white table.
Pick up the metal fork that is just below the egg on the round table.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a left and begin walking to the door, hang another left before the counter and walk up to the frying pan on the kitchen counter.
Place the fork handle down into the frying pan that is to the right of the large metal pot on the kitchen counter.
Pick up the frying pan with the metal fork in it.
Turn around and walk back over to the round white table.
Place the frying pan with the fork in it onto the round table to the left of the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with a fork in it on a round table.
